QuestData.Title: Who Did This?
QuestData.Description: Sabotage! It had to be. The whole fortress magazine exploded. The Horde must've gotten someone inside...$B$B$C, if you've the stones to rush into that burning nightmare... look for some clues as to who did this to us. The General will want to know! Look for a Horde corpse in the wreckage and get to the bottom of this disaster...
QuestData.LogDescription: Look for a Horde corpse within Bael'dun Keep.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Look for a Horde corpse within Bael'dun Keep in Southern Barrens.
QuestData.RewardText: <One smoldering corpse stands out amidst the carnage. The dead goblin clutches the schematics of the fortress in his lifeless hand...>$B$B<The Bilgewater Cartel goblins. They did this!>
